headline: Women-owned Suppliers Boost Corporate Revenue by 2.2% in Southeast Asia
summary: The American Chamber of Commerce in Singapore (AmChamSG), in collaboration with Accenture and WEConnect International, launched 'The Diversity Dividend: Why it Pays to Engage Women Owned Businesses in Southeast Asia' at the 2025 AmChamSG SME ACCelerate Forum with Ms. Yeo Wan Ling, Assistant Secretary-General, National Trades Union Congress (NTUC) and Member of Parliament, Punggol GRC.
